4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goat, goldfish
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, march, september, october
1. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
2. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the doctor##5
3. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the goat##2
4. the doctor is somewhere to the right of the musician##5
5. the person who's birthday is in october is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
7. the musician is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in may##7
8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
9. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |      4       |
| Job         | librarian | musician | doctor    | photographer |
| Pet         | frog      | goldfish | dog       | goat         |
| Birthday   | september | october    | march | may     |

