3. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
4. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the left of the fan of indie##5
5. the person eating corn is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
6. the person eating carrot is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
7. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching musical movies##5
8. the fan of indie is somewhere to the right of the fan of electronic##5
9. the person watching musical movies is not the fan of d&b##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Food          | apricot | cucumber | corn          | carrot  |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | d&b      | electronic    | indie   |
| Movie-Genre         | thriller | adventure  | musical | martial-arts |

